Dialogue: 2,0:01:15.81,0:01:23.74,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感觉不会再相见
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.74,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}運命が笑う
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.74,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}命运在嘲笑
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.10,0:01:31.91,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}臨界点突破してんだ
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.10,0:01:31.91,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}突破临界点
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.72,OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}限界なら既に去って
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.72,OP_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}界限已被清除
